        "Description": "Your client is the old owner of the museum, who wants to buy it back because the new owners are planning to throw out all the representational art and transform it into an &quot;abstract only&quot; museum. Some would call the contract a public service.\r\rYou were hired to lower the price of the property by causing some undesired casualties inside to your heart&apos;s content. Stealing a parked helicopter would also push down the parking cost. You must eliminate the helicopter guards though before leaving...",
